section.section:
Of the Board members:
One shall be a duly qualified and licensed veterinarian;
One shall be an officer of a county humane society;
One shall be an owner of a licensed stable;
One shall be a public member;
One shall be a representative of the Maryland Horse Council, Inc.;
One shall be a representative of the trails and recreational riding community;
One shall represent the organized competitions and shows industry;
One shall represent the Maryland thoroughbred industry;
One shall represent the Maryland standardbred industry;
One shall represent the academic equine community; and
One shall represent the equine trade and support industries.
